				<p>Here are answers to some of the more frequently asked questions (FAQ's) about CHLA. Questions dealing with searching and navigating this site are addressed on the Help page, and a narrative about the project is on our <a href="/collections/chla/about">About</a> page. As always, if you have further questions about this site or its contents please contact us for assistance.</p>

