				<h4 id="acquisitions">Are you soliciting suggestions for new acquisitions?</h4>
				<p>Although the collections in CHLA were methodically selected and reviewed by teams of scholars, we are always open to suggestions for additions. Because of the breadth of subject and scope of years, some titles may emerge that were previously missed, and we would like to know about these. Feel free to contact us with your suggestions.</p>
